    "summary": "Allround Service Manager with strong technical background. Speciality Contact Center Management and service management. 1st Dutch/European MBA Master in Customer Management. Experienced in managing large (300+) national/international/multilingual/multicultural and virtual teams. Realized in multiple organizations best Employee and Customer Satisfaction scores. Recognized as no.1 employer to work for in contact center world. People Manager. Multiple National and International recognitions, like best Contact Center Manager of the Netherlands, 2nd best of the world Contact Center Industry Champion. Experience in implementing multi channel Self Services combined with state of the art knowledge bases (KANA). Usage of my Workforce management and Forecasting methods and skills helped me in managing costs and staffing.\n\nNext to Contact Center Management skills I'm able to transfer service organizations from cost centers to profit centers. Data Mining, finding opportunities, creating initiatives, sharing responsibilities and pro-active approach of process improvement activities continuously energizes the workforce. This creates stable, motivated and passionated self steering teams focussed on quality, costs and sales.\n\nSharing experience and learnings is not new to me. As speaker on national and international conventions, exhibitions, events, site visits and radio I presented several cases and or programs to deliver Customer Excellence.\n\nTo summarize, as an all-round experienced manager, I am able to change a Service Organization to become a profit center. People Management, Financial Management, Sales, Operational Management, Customer Management, all is managed with a drive for result, together with talented and motivated people. The yearly reviews about performance are continuously marked with high rating scores.\n\n",
